#- oropt integration smoke engine: one-ramp nonlinear implicit static, MUMPS
#- direct solver (/IMPL/SOLVER/2), animation carries the fields oropt extracts
#- (/ANIM/ELEM/ENER + VONM + /ANIM/VECT/DISP). Card set mirrors the project's
#- validated fast-mode engine writer (oropt/fastmode.py) plus /IMPL/NONLIN.
/RUN/smoke/1
                 1.0
#
/TFILE
0.0001
#
/PRINT/-1
/MON/ON
#
/ANIM/DT
0. 1.0
/ANIM/VECT/DISP
/ANIM/ELEM/VONM
/ANIM/ELEM/ENER
#
/IMPL/PRINT/NONL/-1
/IMPL/NONLIN/2
         5         0      0.05
/IMPL/SOLVER/2
  0 0 0 0
/IMPL/DTINI
0.5
